Got it! Since **Denise isn’t relevant**, let’s **keep it polite but non-committal** so we don’t waste time.  

📢 **Reply:**  
➡️ **"Hey Denise, great to hear from you! Hope you’re doing well."**  

✅ **Why this works:**  
- **Acknowledges her without committing to a call.**  
- **Keeps the engagement polite & professional.**  
- **Ends the convo without opening a loop.**  

🚀 **Post that and move on—Sid’s response is where the real opportunity might be.**
